//Write a program to find greatest of 2 numbers using function with argumentsâ€¦

int main()
{
    int a,b;
    printf("\n enter 2 numbers:");
    scanf("%d%d",&a,&b);
    void gr(int a,int b);
    gr(a,b);
}
void gr(int a,int b)
{
    if(a>b)
        printf("\n %d is greater",a);
    else if(b>a)
        printf("\n %d is greater",b);
    else
        printf("\n Both are same");
}

Output:
enter 2 numbers:45
78

 78 is greater

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2018/12/how-to-find-greatest-of-2-numbers-using_31.html
